---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import nurseImage from "../../assets/nurse.png";
---

<section class="reveal bg-white px-4 py-10 md:px-10 lg:px-40">
  <div class="mx-auto flex w-full max-w-[1200px] flex-col gap-10 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:gap-20">
    <div class="reveal reveal-left flex flex-1 flex-col gap-8 text-left">
      <div class="reveal delay-1 flex flex-col gap-4">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-black leading-tight tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
          <span class="text-primary">Bienve</span>nido a Cuida<span class="text-primary">Link</span>
        </h1>
        <h2 class="max-w-xl text-lg font-normal leading-relaxed text-slate-600">
          La tecnologia que une a la familia. Monitorea la seguridad y el bienestar de tus seres queridos en tiempo real, desde cualquier lugar.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal delay-2 flex flex-wrap gap-4 pt-4">
        <img src="/public/svg.svg" alt="Google Play" class="h-16 w-auto" />
      </div>

      <div class="reveal delay-3 flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-slate-500">
        <span class="icon-pop material-symbols-outlined text-lg text-primary">check_circle</span>
        <span>Registro gratuito y seguro</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="reveal reveal-right delay-1 w-full flex-1 md:mx-auto md:max-w-[600px] lg:max-w-[500px]">
      <div class="animate-pulsing relative aspect-square w-full overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] bg-slate-100 shadow-2xl">
        <Image
          alt="Enfermera cuidando a una paciente mayor"
          class=" h-full w-full object-cover"
          src={nurseImage}
          loading="eager"
        />

        <div class="absolute bottom-6 left-5 right-5 flex items-center gap-4 rounded-xl  bg-white/75 p-4 shadow-lg backdrop-blur-sm transition-transform duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
          <div class="icon-pop flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white/25 text-primary">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined">handshake</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">Enfoque en Confianza Familiar</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Acceso exclusivo y seguro para tu circulo familiar de confianza.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
